Name: Trouble Travel TT
About the game: An easy-to-play platformer-quest, invites the player to go through the hard way of a person who got lost in a nonexistent city. In which strange things happen. Solve riddles, keep up on time, run while you can. Perhaps you can get out. But carefully, on each level you are expected by traps and complex timings that you will have to observe!
